trans-unit.source: Provides a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.

The WebPartTransformerCollection class is a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects, typically used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection> object to manage a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects for a connection.
The transformers related to a Web Parts connection can be retrieved through the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnection.Transformers%2A> property.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection"></xref> class.
Adds an object to the end of the collection.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> to be added to the end of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection"></xref>.
The index at which transformer has been added.
Returns a value indicating whether a particular transformer exists in the collection.

The Contains method enables you to check a particular <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> object and determine whether it is part of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> object.
A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> that is checked to determine whether it is in the collection.
A Boolean value that indicates whether a particular transformer is in the collection.
Copies the collection to an array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects.

The CopyTo method is useful when you want to assemble a custom array that can contain all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection> collection, a subset of those objects, or a superset of those objects.
An array of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> objects to contain the copied collection.
The starting point in the array at which to place the collection contents.
Returns the position of a particular member in the collection.
A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> that is a member of the collection.
An integer that indicates the position of a particular object in the collection.
Inserts a transformer into the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformerCollection"></xref> collection at the specified index.
The zero-based index at which a value should be inserted.
The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartTransformer"></xref> to insert.
